cc:Work.dc:title: Old Ornate Asian Frame
cc:Work.dc:description: Found this on the title page of a 1888 Japanese book. The title is tall and narrow because Japanese can be written vertically. So you'll either have to rotate your text or be creative in some other way. I just thought it was a really beautiful old ornate Asian Style frame that I had to synthesize it so that I could share it. \n\nI just realized now that it is quite phallic. Wonder if that was intentional?
